    "Therefore, to examine whether the impact of green bond issuance on ER is heterogeneous with managers' ability, we first calculated the average education level of all managerial members within the enterprise as the proxy for the manager's ability.",
    "We then divided the total sample into two subgroups according to the average value (i.e., one group with a relatively high education level and the other with a relatively low education level).",
    "We regress green bond issuance on ER on these two subgroups, and Table 9 shows the estimation results.",
    "The coefficients of Green × Time in Columns (32)-(33) are 8.5201 and 8.4046, respectively, at the 5% significance level.",
    "The coefficients of Green × Time in Columns (34)-(35) are insignificant, which validates our previous ideas."
  ],
